      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"meaning\" stuff feels like such a cope though. Like, if I spend my whole life working and loving and struggling just to have it all erased by entropy... it's not just small, it's actually absurd. It feels more like a cruel joke than a gift. If there's no objective point to any of it, why keep participating in the struggle? It just seems like a lot of unnecessary effort for a result that's zero.",
